The entire colony flourishes with vegetative growth throughout the year, though it is more pronounced in summer. The evergreen woodland is rich in organic matter, fertile soil, and biological resources. It is highly suitable for efficient ecological forestry and moderately suitable for agricultural practices.

Gemstones are the most beautiful and valuable type of minerals in rocks. They are bright in color, crystalline in texture, highly lustrous, hard and durable, though scarcely available. This place is suitable for reasonable development, mainly for the jewelry industry.
